      "title": "Start negotiations Resolve political turmoil - IMF",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The organization hopes for a solution to the political turmoil in Sri Lanka by allowing the resumption of negotiations on the loan package provided by the International Monetary Fund to Sri Lanka.",
        "\"We hope to resolve the current situation to allow us to resume our dialogue on an IMF-sponsored program,\" the IMF said in a statement."
      ],
